ess of whether they are receiving an acetylcholinesterase inhibitor.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/162279/', '', 'Ketotifen, Levocetirizine, Cetirizine, Trimethobenzamide, Azelastine', 'Aducanumab', 1767369485);
